|comments= 

So the idea came out of seeing "pataphysics" and thinking it said "pastaphysics" and then thinking about what a department of pastaphysics would actually be. Then I started writing and it got a lot more serious than I expected.

A little explored part of the Foundation, I think. Hope y'all enjoy it.

]]
